          "text": "DECIMAL",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", or "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "FLOAT",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", depending on the precision required for the credit calculation. The function returns a single numeric value representing the remaining credit."
